prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: About 3 weeks ago I experienced a drive by shooting. I was at a neighbors home we're we were just talking about things having a normal conversation. things started to get crazy in the area thought. It involved a drive by shooting. I am very grateful to have been able to get through with no issues. I know my friends weren't hurt as well. Overall it was a crazy situation to experience.
